{
  "stem": "2539.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed with the shoemaker, by the way, until their Soviets came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They liberated me in Berezovka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to this day, I think there were either two-- two reasons she didn't take me-- number one, because she wanted to save my life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because these Ukrainian partisans, some of them were terribly anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They killed the Jews themselves.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or, maybe she thought I was too young.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe she thought that I'll get raped by them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She wanted to protect me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think she wanted to-- my opinion was, because her auntie loved me so much, and loved her so much, there must have been something in that letter that told the woman, save that girl.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she saved me by not letting me join the partisans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went back to Berezovka.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I stayed with the shoemaker and his wife.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a sister there, and a little child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, there were-- the Soviets, the-- the Germans were departing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, to my amazement, the last Germans that left Berezovka saluted me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you see, I was hiding the fact that I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, nobody knew in the village.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because I also spoke very fluent Ukrainian, don't forget-- very fluent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I spoke beautiful Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went to Ukrainian school when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody learned Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because Poland was gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was Ukraine now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I have a gift for languages like nobody's business-- like nobody I know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I speak 15 languages-- fluently!",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I write.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I read, and I speak them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So of course, they-- they thought I was Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In any case, the point was that there were officers passing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "First there were-- oh, the Germans saluted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They boarded their horses, and saluted me, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The last ones left on horses.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
